The king of the trolls has stolen the Minotaur's most prized
possession and sent him on a rampage.  Return to him his
property.

This is a mid-level quest involving killing some fairly strong
monsters in locations not suited to complete freedom. Some of
what was here has had to be recreated, but the feel is hopefully
the same.

The location of this quest is no longer obvious and will require
lots of searching on the part of the questors.
